Vol / Page: 14
Edition:
Quote: There must have been about 100 acres of pasture on the steep hillside, with here and there a clump of bush and quite an area of devil-weed. It was all manuka here, about six to seven feet high, but gave way to devil-weed and fern in the gully, as we crossed over onto the first ridge.
